	<h1 class="title">我是如何用不到500元在上海老洋房里 Airbnb 了一晚上</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37533/small/37533.jpg?1421717946" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐冰蕊</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-14 13:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7348/medium/7348.jpg?1436689585" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


